snippet.title: Syrup Movie Trailer -- Amber Heard, Shiloh Fernandez & Kellan Lutz
snippet.description:
Syrup Official Movie Trailer with Amber Heard, Shiloh Fernandez, Kellan Lutz and Brittany Snow
http://bit.ly/SubClevverNews - Subscribe Now!
http://Facebook.com/ClevverNews - Like Us!
http://Twitter.com/ClevverNews - Follow Us!
Our first look at Amber Heard and Shiloh Fernandez in their new movie! We have the trailer!
Hey hey  guys -- happy Friday and thanks for keeping your computers locked on Clevver News. 
The teaser trailer for the upcoming film Syrup has JUST hit the web, and the movie looks pretty darn great. 
Syrup stars Shiloh Fernandez, Amber Heard, Kellan Lutz AND Brittany Snow.  Take a look:
(CLIP)
The movie is an adaptation of the popular novel of the same name by author Max Barry.  The film centers around a slacker named Scat -- played by Shiloh, who hatches a million-dollar idea.  In order to see his vision come to life though, he must learn to trust her attractive corporate counterpart named SIX, played by Amber. 
Kellan will take on the role of Sneaky Pete and Brittany Snow plays the character of a gal named THREE. 
As of now, there is no slated release date -- but I'm hearing later this year or early next year. 
What do you guys think of this trailer.... Does the film look interesting to you?
Let me know all of your thoughts and opinions by writing out a comment below and then make sure you hit that subscribe button for all the latest news on your favorite celebs, all day -- everyday.
In Hollywood, I'm your host Katie Krause, enjoy your weekend.... Do something fun and I'll see you back here on Monday!
